Our journey to Net Zero has been shaped by ambition, innovation and a deep respect for the planet. With EDGE Advanced Certification and recognition from the Indian Green Building Council’s Net Zero Waste Platinum (Operations) program, we have embedded sustainability into every layer of our operations from low-flow water fixtures and composting systems to retrofitting legacy infrastructure and running on 100% green energy.

We are also proud to be part of Beyond Green, a global portfolio of properties known for their environmental and community commitment.

This World Environment Day, we celebrate our progress and reaffirm our mission to #BeatPlasticPollution, proving that true luxury lies in responsibility, and that sustainability is and always will be our main promise.

#TheLeela #TheLeelaBengaluru #WorldEnvironmentDay
